My Duplicants may slip and fall on wet surfaces, and Duplicants with bionic systems can experience disruptive glitching.\n\nI can help my colony avoid undue <link=\"STRESS\">Stress</link> and potential injury by using the <b>Mop Tool</b> {Hotkey/Mop} to clean up spills. Building <link=\"REQUIREMENTCLASSTOILETTYPE\">Toilets</link> and <link=\"GUNKEMPTIER\">Gunk Extractors</link> can help minimize the incidence of spills.